data.description:
Welcome home to this stylish 3-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom gem in the heart of Killeen! Newly upgraded with modern vinyl flooring, this residence offers a spacious living room that seamlessly connects to a separate kitchen and dining area. Upstairs, three generously sized bedrooms provide a peaceful retreat, including a master suite with a private en-suite bathroom. Additionally, discover an additional open area upstairs that could serve as an extra living space or a game room, adding versatility to the home. The property is equipped with a top-notch security system for your peace of mind.
Conveniently located near amenities and schools. With a quick 10 minute drive to Fort Cavazos formerly known as Fort Hood, this home is a perfect blend of style and practicality. Don't miss the chance to make it yours – schedule a showing today!
